description: Retrieves information about an override to an on-call rotation.

parameters.name: RotationId
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the overridden rotation to retrieve information about.

parameters.name: RotationOverrideId
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the on-call rotation override to retrieve information about.

nested_items.name: RotationOverrideId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the override to an on-call rotation.

nested_items.name: RotationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the on-call rotation that was overridden.

nested_items.name: NewContactIds
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Names (ARNs) of the contacts assigned to the override of the on-call rotation.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The date and time when the override goes into effect.

nested_items.name: EndTime
nested_items.description: The date and time when the override ends.

nested_items.name: CreateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time when the override was created.
